@startuml
title D2 - Diagrama de Clases: Base de Conocimiento Clínica

skinparam classAttributeIconSize 0
skinparam packageStyle rectangle
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam linetype ortho

package "Base de Conocimiento" {

  class Species {
    +id: int
    +name: string
    +description: string
    +is_active: bool
  }

  class Disease {
    +id: int
    +name: string
    +description: string
    +species_id: int
    +is_active: bool
  }

  class Symptom {
    +id: int
    +name: string
    +key: string
    +species_id: int
    +is_active: bool
  }

  class ClinicalVariable {
    +id: int
    +name: string
    +key: string
    +unit: string
    +species_id: int
    +is_active: bool
  }

  class FactDefinition {
    +id: int
    +fact_key: string
    +label: string
    +fact_type: string
    +species_id: int
    +symptom_id: int
    +clinical_variable_id: int
    +is_active: bool
  }

  class ClinicalProbability {
    +id: int
    +disease_id: int
    +symptom_id: int
    +clinical_variable_id: int
    +fact_key: string
    +probability: float
  }

  class RiskLevel {
    +id: int
    +name: string
    +description: string
    +priority: int
  }

  class InferenceRule {
    +id: int
    +name: string
    +description: string
    +disease_id: int
    +risk_level_id: int
    +weight: float
    +is_active: bool
  }

  class RuleCondition {
    +id: int
    +rule_id: int
    +fact_key: string
    +operator: string
    +expected_value: string
  }

  class KnowledgeSource {
    +id: int
    +title: string
    +authors: string
    +year: int
    +source_type: string
    +url: string
  }

  class RuleReference {
    +id: int
    +rule_id: int
    +knowledge_source_id: int
    +note: string
  }
}

Species "1" -- "0..*" Disease : restringe
Species "1" -- "0..*" Symptom : define
Species "1" -- "0..*" ClinicalVariable : define
Species "1" -- "0..*" FactDefinition : valida

Disease "1" -- "0..*" InferenceRule : posee reglas
Disease "1" -- "0..*" ClinicalProbability : usa probabilidades

Symptom "0..1" -- "0..*" FactDefinition : puede originar
ClinicalVariable "0..1" -- "0..*" FactDefinition : puede originar

Symptom "0..1" -- "0..*" ClinicalProbability : evidencia
ClinicalVariable "0..1" -- "0..*" ClinicalProbability : evidencia

RiskLevel "1" -- "0..*" InferenceRule : clasifica
InferenceRule "1" -- "1..*" RuleCondition : compuesta por

KnowledgeSource "1" -- "0..*" RuleReference : sustenta
InferenceRule "1" -- "0..*" RuleReference : referenciada por

note right of FactDefinition
Catálogo maestro de hechos clínicos.
Permite validar síntomas y variables
según la especie del paciente.
end note

note right of InferenceRule
Representa una regla IF-THEN
del conocimiento clínico.
Cada regla apunta a una enfermedad
y a un nivel de riesgo.
end note

note bottom of ClinicalProbability
Almacena las probabilidades
P(evidencia | enfermedad)
utilizadas por Naive Bayes.
end note

@enduml